== 乐队历史 ==
阿加·沃克曼在美国[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[尤金市|尤金市]]读高中时便开始创作歌曲，而后她搬到了美国加州[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]开始了她的单独表演。沃克曼曾经希望最终能建立一支乐队，这个愿望在她在2005年的一次表演后实现了，米克·佩纳同意与他和瑞奇·克勒一起唱歌<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2014/Feb/13/nico-vega-imagine-dragons-san-diego/|title=Nico Vega aiming for wider reach|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2014-02-13|last=Matthews|first=Edward|publisher=UTSanDiego.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224224213/http://www.utsandiego.com/news/2014/Feb/13/nico-vega-imagine-dragons-san-diego/|archivedate=2014-02-24}}</ref>。乐队自称为尼科维加乐队。然而，2007年米克离开了乐队去追求表演和享受父亲的乐队。在那个关键时间节点，丹·潘德作为新的鼓手加入了乐队而后成为乐队持续创新的动力源泉。

尼科维加乐队逐渐赢得了震撼现场乐队的评价，乐队还与[[Gavin_Rossdale|Gavin Rossdale]]（2009）<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://racketmag.com/music/nico-vega-and-gavin-rossdale-hob-anaheim-show-review/|title=Nico Vega and Gavin Rossdale – HOB Anaheim – Show Review | Racket Magazine|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2009-06-16|publisher=Racketmag.com|archive-date=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307224905/http://racketmag.com/music/nico-vega-and-gavin-rossdale-hob-anaheim-show-review/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、Neon Trees (2009, 2012)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.boiseweekly.com/Cobweb/archives/2012/06/09/neon-trees-show-boise-love-and-affection|title=Neon Trees Show Boise Love and Affection | Cobweb|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2012-06-09|last=Merrill|first=Amy|publisher=Boise Weekly|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307223952/http://www.boiseweekly.com/Cobweb/archives/2012/06/09/neon-trees-show-boise-love-and-affection|archive-date=2014-03-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[Manic_Street_Preachers|Manic Street Preachers]] (2009-2010)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://spinningplatters.com/2009/09/25/show-review-manic-street-preachers-and-nico-vega-at-the-fillmore-92409/|title=Show Review: Manic Street Preachers and Nico Vega at The Fillmore, 9/24/09|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2009-09-25|publisher=Spinningplatters.com|archive-date=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307225155/http://spinningplatters.com/2009/09/25/show-review-manic-street-preachers-and-nico-vega-at-the-fillmore-92409/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[Metric_(band)|Metric]] (2010)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.411mania.com/music/concerts/134563|title=Music - Metric w/ Nico Vega - Hollywood Palladium, Los Angeles, CA (03.26.10)|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=|publisher=411mania.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308013915/http://www.411mania.com/music/concerts/134563|archivedate=2014-03-08}}</ref>、She Wants Revenge (2011)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://kdhx.org/blog/2011/06/08/concert-review-she-wants-revenge-and-nico-vega-cook-at-the-firebird-tuesday-june-7/|title=Concert review: She Wants Revenge and Nico Vega cook at the Firebird, Tuesday, June 7 : KDHX Blog|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2011-06-08|publisher=Kdhx.org|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828143043/http://kdhx.org/blog/2011/06/08/concert-review-she-wants-revenge-and-nico-vega-cook-at-the-firebird-tuesday-june-7/|archivedate=2013-08-28}}</ref>、[[Blondie_(band)|Blondie]] (2011)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.dallasobserver.com/2011-09-29/music/blondie-nico-vega/full/|title=Blondie, Nico Vega|accessdate=2014-05-14|author=Ray Cummings|date=2011-09-29|publisher=Dallas Observer|archive-date=2014-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307224626/http://www.dallasobserver.com/2011-09-29/music/blondie-nico-vega/full/|dead-url=no}}</ref>以及[[Imagine_Dragons|Imagine Dragons]] (2010, 2013, 2014)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.heraldextra.com/entertainment/music/nico-vega-in-sync-with-imagine-dragons-at-uccu-center/article_33927efc-179e-5944-96fa-f850d32ec2fb.html|title=Nico Vega in sync with Imagine Dragons at UCCU Center : The Ticket|accessdate=2014-05-14|author=Cody Clark|date=2013-05-16|publisher=Heraldextra.com|archive-date=2014-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614222618/http://www.heraldextra.com/entertainment/music/nico-vega-in-sync-with-imagine-dragons-at-uccu-center/article_33927efc-179e-5944-96fa-f850d32ec2fb.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>等一起巡回演唱。此外，乐队还曾与毫无疑问乐队开展过合作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.indierockreviews.com/2012/11/video-nico-vega-we-are-the-art/|title=Video: Nico Vega - "We Are The Art"|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2011-09-27|publisher=Indie Rock Reviews|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316065936/http://www.indierockreviews.com/2012/11/video-nico-vega-we-are-the-art/|archive-date=2014-03-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 2009发行专辑《尼科·维加》 ===
[16][17]尼科维加前期发表过一些独立的EPS和自己录制的视频将他们的音乐推广开来。2009年，尼科维加在[[MySpace|MySpace]]唱片发布了他们的第一张专辑。这张专辑由蒂姆·埃德加（乐队的朋友）和琳达·佩里（Pink，关史蒂芬妮，克里斯蒂娜·阿奎莱拉）联合制作。琳达制作了专辑中的《所以很新鲜》、《木娃娃》和《重力》这三首歌。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gigwise.com/features/50435/ready-for-another-gear-change---nico-vega|title=Ready For Another Gear Change - Nico Vega|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2009-04-14|publisher=Gigwise|archive-date=2014-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224111354/http://www.gigwise.com/features/50435/ready-for-another-gear-change---nico-vega|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/nico-vega-mw0000808526/credits|title=Nico Vega - Nico Vega | Credits|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2009-02-03|publisher=AllMusic|archive-date=2013-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130203023647/http://www.allmusic.com/album/nico-vega-mw0000808526/credits|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这张专辑由乍得·布雷克（黑键，雪儿克罗）混音。2013年，尼科维加发布迷你专辑《Fury Oh Fury 》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/nico-vega-unleash-heavy-hooks-on-fury-oh-fury-ep-premiere-20130130|title=Nico Vega Unleash Heavy Hooks on 'Fury Oh Fury' EP Premiere | Music News|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2013-01-30|publisher=Rolling Stone|archive-date=2014-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228175224/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/nico-vega-unleash-heavy-hooks-on-fury-oh-fury-ep-premiere-20130130|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并重新发布了单曲《野兽》，《野兽》发布在了一款游戏的音乐单中，因此获得了极高的知名度，得到了超过播放和下载总数超过500万次。鼓手丹·潘德获得了与安迪·萨默斯（警察）合作项目的机会。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://drumheadmag.com/news/616-nico-vega-drummer-dan-epand-checks-in.html|title=Nico Vega Drummer Dan Epand Checks In|accessdate=2014-07-23|date=2014-06-22|publisher=Drumheadmag.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140726114625/http://drumheadmag.com/news/616-nico-vega-drummer-dan-epand-checks-in.html|archive-date=2014-07-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JE1k5rAgWLQ|title=Circa Zero Performs "Levitation"|accessdate=2014-07-23|date=2014-04-30|publisher=YouTube|archive-date=2014-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140430162536/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JE1k5rAgWLQ&gl=US&hl=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2014发行专辑《奔向光明》 ===
乐队的第二张专辑《奔向光明》是于２０１４年７月２２日发布在Five Seven Music上的。<ref name="nicovega.com">{{Cite web|url=http://nicovega.com/press-release-nico-vega-launches-new-single-i-believe-kicks-off-tour-with-imagine-dragons/|title=PRESS RELEASE: Nico Vega Launches New Single "I Believe" Kicks Off Tour with Imagine Dragons|accessdate=2014-05-14|author=|date=2014-02-10|publisher=Nico Vega|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809213802/http://nicovega.com/press-release-nico-vega-launches-new-single-i-believe-kicks-off-tour-with-imagine-dragons/|archivedate=2017年8月9日|df=}}</ref> 这张专辑由[[丹·雷诺兹|丹·雷诺兹]]、托尼·霍弗和蒂姆·埃德加共同制作的。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6165305/nico-vega-premiere-lead-to-light-imagine-dragons-dan-reynolds?utm_source=twitter|title=Nico Vega Premieres Hook-Filled New LP 'Lead to Light' (Listen)|accessdate=2014-07-23|date=|publisher=Billboard|archive-date=2016-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120220343/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6165305/nico-vega-premiere-lead-to-light-imagine-dragons-dan-reynolds?utm_source=twitter|dead-url=no}}</ref> 单曲《I Believe (Get Over Yourself》是由丹·雷诺兹创作的歌词。<ref name="nicovega.com">{{Cite web|url=http://nicovega.com/press-release-nico-vega-launches-new-single-i-believe-kicks-off-tour-with-imagine-dragons/|title=PRESS RELEASE: Nico Vega Launches New Single "I Believe" Kicks Off Tour with Imagine Dragons|accessdate=2014-05-14|author=|date=2014-02-10|publisher=Nico Vega|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809213802/http://nicovega.com/press-release-nico-vega-launches-new-single-i-believe-kicks-off-tour-with-imagine-dragons/|archivedate=2017年8月9日|df=}}</ref> 尼科维加在VH1里的《Big Morning Buzz Live》节目中现场表演了《I Believe (Get Over Yourself)》。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.vh1.com/video/misc/1038395/i-believe-get-over-yourself-big-morning-buzz-live.jhtml#id=1727121|title="I Believe (Get Over Yourself) (Big Morning Buzz Live)" by Nico Vega | Show Performance|accessdate=2014-05-14|author=|date=2014-05-06|publisher=VH1.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507001403/http://www.vh1.com/video/misc/1038395/i-believe-get-over-yourself-big-morning-buzz-live.jhtml#id=1727121|archivedate=2014-05-07}}</ref> 并在以拖车为主要特色的美国电视节目《Girls第四季》上演示了由She Wants Revenge成员参与作词的录影带Lightning。[[NPR|NPR]]通过All Songs首映了录影带《I'm On Fire》，并经考虑后决定提供该录影带的免费下载通道。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/allsongs/2014/05/13/312143989/new-mix-premieres-from-nico-vega-joe-henry-more|title=New Mix: Premieres From Nico Vega, Joe Henry, More : All Songs Considered|accessdate=2014-05-14|date=2014-05-10|publisher=NPR|archive-date=2014-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140514030502/http://www.npr.org/blogs/allsongs/2014/05/13/312143989/new-mix-premieres-from-nico-vega-joe-henry-more|dead-url=no}}</ref> 今日美国首映了录影带《No Home》。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/07/16/song-premiere-nico-vega-opens-the-doors-to-no-home/12755975/|title=Song premiere: Nico Vega opens the doors to 'No Home'|accessdate=2014-07-23|date=2014-07-17|publisher=Usatoday.com|archive-date=2014-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140721055748/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/music/2014/07/16/song-premiere-nico-vega-opens-the-doors-to-no-home/12755975/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

